title: DS4G : Emission Factor
description: OVERVIEWThe Environmental Insights Explorer team at Google is keen to gather insights on ways to improve calculations of global emissions factors of sub-national regions.The ultimate goal of this challenge is to test if calculations of emission factor using remote sensing technique are possible.
